napc_memeql Compare two memory regions.
napc_mzero Zero out memory region.

napc_removeLogHandlerFunction Remove a log handler function

napc_getRandomBit Create a random bit value.

napc_mzero
View definition on github

Clear memory section.

Function Protoype 

void napc_mzero(
    void *    data,
    napc_size data_size
);

Rationale

It's cumbersome to write memset(data, 0, data_size).

Parameter

data
Buffer to be zero'd out.
data_size
Size of data buffer.

Example Usage 

char buffer[512];

// clear data buffer
napc_mzero(buffer, sizeof(buffer));
